Rythmbox Prehear plugin

Description
===========

This plugin provides an easy way to select songs without stopping the current
one. Typically, the new secondary audio output could be directed to a headset 
while the main output continue playing on the main audio card.

Requirement
===========
You should have the following requirement in order to use this plugin
- either an audio card with 2 independent audio output (most audio card only
  have one output)
- either 2 audio cards.

You can use some USB audio card, they are cheep and very well supported by 
GNU/Linux

Installation
============
Execute the installation script with the following command:

  ./install.sh
  

Usage
=====


Uninstall
=========
Execute the remove script :

  ./uninstall.sh

